comments.content: Looks like a customized Trade Gothic (alternative g, a and l).

If you know what you’re looking for, always [do a search](http://web.archive.org/web/20080827234202/http:/www.google.com/search?q=site:typophile.com%20morgan%20stanley) first. ;^)

This is a [custom designed word mark](http://web.archive.org/web/20080827234202/http:/typophile.com/node/30155).
